# How to show Downloads file on the desktop
# 1. Change the location to .config directory
command --> cd .config
# 2. Open user-dirs.dirs file
command --> gedit user-dirs.dirs
# 3. Change the path of Desktop to Downloads
# 4. Save user-dirs.dirs file 
# 5. Reboot your system 
# 6. Now the files in the Download directory will be shown on the Desktop
